&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to join the administration team within the Crisis Response Service at Eastbourne DGH.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Coordination Support Administrator provides invaluable support to the shift coordinator and community staff during core working hours, ensuring smooth service delivery . The role requires excellent organisational and ICT skills, as well as the ability to remain calm, professional and methodical in a busy office environment. The successful candidate will have substantial administration experience and enjoy working as part of a multi-disciplinary team. If you have experience managing an office and supervising staff, and enjoy the challenge of working in a developing team, then we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Felicity Lea, Team Lead &amp; Occupational Therapist, Email address: felicity.lea1@nhs.net Telephone number: 07815 698022&lt;/p&gt;
